videos.headline: Smart: Georgia 'still a work in progress' after winning SEC East
videos.description: Kirby Smart says No. 6 Georgia kept battling but has to get better after defeating No. 9 Kentucky 34-17 to win the SEC East title.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Smart: Georgia 'still a work in progress' after winning SEC East) 2018/11/03
